Hide
Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Colour 0,$111
Colour 1,$F40
Colour 2,$2DF
Colour 3,$FFF
Cls 0
Ink 1
Bar 0,0 To 23,23
Get Bob 1,0,0 To 24,24
Cls 0
Ink 2
Bar 0,0 To 23,23
Get Bob 2,0,0 To 24,24
Cls 0
Bob 1,140,80,1
Bob 2,152,80,2
Wait Vbl
Pen 3
Paper 0
If Bob Col(1,2 To 2)
   Locate 8,16
   Print "The bobs are touching!"
Else
   Locate 8,16
   Print "The bobs are apart."
End If
Wait Key
